{"id":232774103,"title":"目光總是能改變我","content":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfR.jpg\n\n目光照射\n牆面映出的影子\n那算是我嗎？\n\n失真的成像\n被不同的凹透鏡\n聚焦出無數個面貌\n\n縮小光圈、拉長焦距\n調慢快門、闔上蓋子\n我錄下機械組合的聲響\n縱使偶爾有點刺耳\n\n反覆播放回憶\n你們說的我\n跟我鏡子裡的一樣嗎\n我能夠做點什麼嗎\n就像比手影那樣\n我看著牆壁擺動身軀\n卻忘了自己的模樣\n\n我想那不是我\n只是目光總是能改變我\n\n-\n照片攝於高雄市立美術館\n以光纖界：徐永旭的藝術世界\n-\n喜歡可以追蹤我的IG\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/B6lhs1LDghs/?igshid=zpf20uhk8sua","excerpt":"目光照射，牆面映出的影子，那算是我嗎？失真的成像，被不同的凹透鏡，聚焦出無數個面貌，縮小光圈、拉長焦距，調慢快門、闔上蓋子，我錄下機械組合的聲響，縱使偶爾有點刺耳，反覆播放回憶，你們說的我，跟我鏡子裡","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["創作","文字","詩文","心情","詩"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"冬片微微","department":"anothert","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfR.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"e4951cb3-c050-4493-b364-3ef1eece363f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfRl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfRl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfRl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z"},{"id":"e4951cb3-c050-4493-b364-3ef1eece363f","url":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfR.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/2GYtLfR","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/2GYtLfRl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-27T18:51:10.067Z"}],"postAvatar":""}